OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloud
OL,6,Fcontinuing to thin throughout the
OL,7,Fevening allowing some lengthy clear
OL,8,Fspells to develop. Under the clear
OL,9,Fspells some mist and fog patches
OL,10,Fdeveloping, especially towards dawn.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FMist and fog clearing
OL,13,Fduring the morning allowing some good
OL,14,Fspells of sunshine to develop.
OL,15,FSunshine often hazy in the west with
OL,16,Fthicker cloud arriving here later.
OL,17,FFeeling very mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
