OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FRain
OL,6,Fmoving across the region on Thursday
OL,7,Fbefore turning drier and brighter on
OL,8,FFriday. Further rain likely later on
OL,9,FSaturday. Temperatures returning to
OL,10,Fnearer average.
